info.name: Purple Neon City Aesthetic - Roblox Background
info.description: I like this one! It's a pretty....city Don't be surprised if it's more low quality than normal, if you just look at the thumbnail- Found this from Wallpaper Flare tags: aesthetic neon glitch purple
info.additionalInfo: Basic info: Don't spam with anything "/e" in the comments that's obnoxious :/. Also thanks to my friend DittoDino/BoopBop for helping me make these fun styles :D Please leave suggestions for themes in my comments, it's very fun for me and I'll make it as best as you desire! Lastly, enjoy the theme :) ︶꒦꒷♡꒷꒦︶ Support: "Hey why's the quality so low." I have to limit the amount of data I use on Stylish, if it's too high quality (means high pixels), that will add more data onto the style and most likely go over the limit Stylish uses and will say I cannot use it. Or sometimes Stylish does that automatically to my style instead of telling me - I am still a newbie to HTML coding so I won't be perfect with making these styles I don't know 3/4 the time what anything is I just wanna have fun making these, once I learn more I will add more to this support section.
